title: Fruit, There It Is
description: Conan discusses which cereal mascot he could take in a fight while speaking with Maggie from New Hampshire. Then he’s introduced to a very cute bunny and the idea of transforming a house into a cafe while talking to Keri from Pennsylvania.
author: conaf@teamcoco.com (Team Coco & Earwolf)
